{"word":"G5399 - φοβέω - phobéō - fob-eh'-o - Be afraid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φοβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phobéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fob-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be afraid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயப்படு, பயந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to be put to flight, to flee"},{"paragraph":"2. to fear, be afraid"},{"paragraph":"3. to reverence, venerate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>; to <i>frighten</i>, that is, (passively) to <i>be alarmed</i>; by analogy to <i>be in awe</i> of, that is, <i>revere:</i> - be (+ sore) afraid, fear (exceedingly), reverence.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5399/5399\">G5399</a>, <a href=\"#/G5400/5400\">G5400</a>, <a href=\"#/G5401/5401\">G5401</a>"}]}